&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Client Onboarding and Implementation: &lt;/strong&gt;Support the client onboarding process, from leadership conversations, clinical workflow integration, to go-live support.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Training &amp;amp; Customer Support: &lt;/strong&gt;Deliver engaging, hands-on training to healthcare providers and clinical staff (in-person and virtually) and provide support for live customers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Success: &lt;/strong&gt;Build strong, long-term relationships with clients; serve as their go-to resource for best practices, product usage, and troubleshooting. Monitor key success metrics and growth, maintaining high customer satisfaction.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Retention &amp;amp; Growth: &lt;/strong&gt;Drive adoption and expansion opportunities by understanding each client’s unique needs and aligning them with our solutions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
